              "id": "QUE64904",
              "question": "Which of the following is an effect the increasing aging population will have on society?\n\u003cbr /\u003e",
              "order": "randomized",
              "presenterType": "RadioGroup",
              "presenterConfig": {
                "numberFormat": "none"
              },
              "choices": [
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "The younger generations will be forced to interact more with the elderly."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "There will be a decreased demand for social services, since modern people are healthier."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "People will retire earlier, resulting in a younger workforce."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_4",
                  "content": "The elderly will contribute to the workforce, creating more available resources."
                }
              ]
            },
            "answerKey": {
              "assessmentType": "multiplechoice",
              "answers": {
                "answer_3": {
                  "score": 0.0,
                  "response": "sider this: As life expectancy increases so does the age of retirement. LO 3.1 Explain how feral, isolated, and institutionalized children help us understand that “society makes us human.”"
                },
                "answer_2": {
                  "score": 0.0,
                  "response": "sider this: A growing elderly population will cause increasing demand for social services. LO 3.1 Explain how feral, isolated, and institutionalized children help us understand that “society makes us human.”"
                },
                "answer_1": {
                  "score": 1.0,
                  "response": "That’s correct!"
                },
                "answer_4": {
                  "score": 0.0,
                  "response": "sider this: Functionalists argue that the elderly need to leave their positions of work to make room for the younger labor force. LO 3.1 Explain how feral, isolated, and institutionalized children help us understand that “society makes us human.” "
                }
              }
